# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The 5 to 9 — .gitignore
# Rule of thumb: the PRODUCT (agents/ skills/ commands/ hooks/ .claude-plugin/)
# is committed. Local/runtime AI state, transcripts, caches, and secrets are NOT.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Local shift state (never commit) ─────────────────────────────────────────
.claude/five-to-nine/
.claude/ralph-loop.local.md
*.local.md

# ── AI-assistant runtime / local artifacts (never commit) ────────────────────
# NOTE: .claude-plugin/ is the plugin manifest dir and IS committed — it is a
# different path from .claude/ (local settings) and is not matched below.
.claude/settings.json
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/*.local.json
.claude/local/
.claude/todos/
.claude/history/
.claude/shell-snapshots/
.claude/statsig/
.claude/projects/
.claude/plugins/
.claude/worktrees/
.codex/
!.codex-plugin/
.aider*
.cursor/
!.cursor-plugin/
.codeium/
.continue/
.specstory/
.windsurf/
.gemini/
.goose/
*.aichat
*.transcript.jsonl
ai-transcripts/
**/agent-*.jsonl
**/*.agent.log
**/*.session.jsonl

# ── Beads: commit the JSONL roadmap export + minimal config; ignore the local
# Dolt DB, bd's git-hook shims, and per-machine runtime. (.beads/ has its own
# .gitignore too; these belt-and-suspenders rules keep the product repo clean.)
.beads/*.db
.beads/*.db-shm
.beads/*.db-wal
.beads/.dolt/
.beads/embeddeddolt/
.beads/cache/
.beads/backup/
.beads/hooks/
.beads/README.md
.beads/interactions.jsonl
.beads/.local_version
.beads/*.lock
.beads-credential-key

# ── Secrets / credentials / env (never commit) ───────────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
id_rsa*
id_ed25519*
secrets.json
.secrets/
credentials.json
*.credentials

# ── Node / tooling ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-error.log
.pnpm-debug.log*

# ── OS / editor noise ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.swp
*~
.idea/
.vscode/

# ── Logs & scratch ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
/tmp/
.scratch/

# Beads / Dolt files (added by bd init)
.dolt/
*.db
.beads/proxieddb/
